Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 看到了嗎 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?看什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再來一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全入冬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 是不是暖和點了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...

