Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...寒風的溫暖.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事呢 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天過後是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 離春天已經不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在春天以前用金平糖把這[瓶]裝滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:02:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話 你可就哪都去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊 早晨起來爸爸還是露著肚皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 我家哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叔叔 今天也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們還是回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我要叫警察了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有進去一步 沒什麼可說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來搗亂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是站在這裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種保育園 誰能放心把孩子留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候來討債的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 這裡是艾草保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利香子的媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你們沒來 我正擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?那個 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼正式文件就以郵遞的方式...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好的 那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請代我告訴利香子請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利香子 說是要退園了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月以來退園的孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是第三個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態的話 家長當然會擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?當然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子自己去搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒啊 有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 堂元君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 都是家裡的和學園祭時沒用完的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來能辦一場開心的聖誕會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要掛這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛我這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君和小鳩的話在屋頂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師 好像很寂寞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說還是那個溫柔的清花老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像非常寂寞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說期限一到 我就會把保育園砸爛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有小孩在也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想有人受傷 就趕緊搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這麼過分的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖浦先生是清花老師的丈夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼丈夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和那位先生談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...他一直站在那裡的話很礙事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你說得動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果好好談談的話 他一定會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了讓你別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要問了 你不要插手這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再有孩子退園的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師又會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事用不著你來擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你什麼都不要做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月以來退園的孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經三個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態的話 家長當然會擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法的話我想清和一定早就去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是勸你別管的好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是去拜託試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 艾草保育園就要沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要去那位先生那裡和他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用雪把它掛滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被雪變成一片潔白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 一起掛起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍也有圓形的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小球把它團團圍起來 然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?在幹什麼啊 土鳩那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的天氣 被子會變得暄騰騰的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋起來很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情的玩耍之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽進暄騰騰的被子裡睡過午覺後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大家互相說 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還能在艾草保育園和大家見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的都是些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有去遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用落葉作畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有挖過白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的義賣會上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多人來捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這所保育園是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凝聚了大家許多 許多的回憶的保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要破壞艾草保育園 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些話等還了債之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道 所以我們會一點點的還
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 和這個人說也無濟於事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那位小哥說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和我說這些也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我去和沖浦先生說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不會聽你說的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓那人的老爹網開一面 根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我先回去了 但是還會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 請不要把艾草保育園...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 今天先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要緊吧 肚子痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 是小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇哥哥也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩跟著走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才救護車 bibobibo地響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是艾草保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闌尾炎?是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會轉告清花老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術也順利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該就不會有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 醫生說了不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是吹的什麼風?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人 就是站在保育園門口的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急發闌尾炎倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闌尾炎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術也順利做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們添麻煩了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊搬走 錢你們還不清的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有商量的餘地了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商量?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了 不像你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?我問你行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 謝謝通知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該放棄了 小清和也從保育園出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我要給那傢伙打什麼電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好談談的話 他一定會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...那位先生沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很快就會康復的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 媽媽 利香子好像退園了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還沒收拾完...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你辛苦了一天 快回去好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始又要忙著做聖誕節的準備了 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是一顆金平糖也沒增加呢 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那位先生很快就能康復了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不好吧 那傢伙好了又會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生...生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說了什麼都別做 可是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩沒有錯 不用在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 在這裡坐一會吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果艾草保育園沒了 大家都會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總在為身邊的人擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又善良 又直率
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩總是很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小鳩這樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我又打起點精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節那天...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:21:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 聖誕會如果還需要什麼東西就跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯

